						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Chennakēśava svāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>SADĀŚIVA DĒVARĀYA.</p>						

						<p>1543 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the Śaka year 1465, Śōbhakṛit Māgha śu, 12, corresponding to 1543 A.D. January 17, Wednesday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It records certain gifts of land made to the Kēśavamūrtti of Yeṛaguḍipāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
